title: Test
summary: This line chart has an x axis representing Year and a y axis representing Total number of stores, with a total of 12 data points.
Overall Total number of stores has increased over the Year.
Total number of stores is slightly increasing from 2008 to 2014, roughly constant from 2014 to 2016, and lastly slightly increasing from 2016 to 2019.
The steepest increase occurs in between the Year 2010 and 2011.
Max Total number of stores about 4915.0 was recorded at Year 2019
Min Total number of stores about 2314.0 was recorded at Year 2008
